    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="问题"><a href="#问题" class="headerlink" title="问题"></a>问题</h2><p>Github托管网站开启Pages的免费网页必须公开代码内容<br>数据不想公开，可以通过Cloudflare同步Github的私有仓库实现</p><h2 id="Github新建私有仓库"><a href="#Github新建私有仓库" class="headerlink" title="Github新建私有仓库"></a>Github新建私有仓库</h2><p>新建，私有abc</p><h2 id="本地仓库"><a href="#本地仓库" class="headerlink" title="本地仓库"></a>本地仓库</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd ~/desktop</span><br><span class="line">mkdir xxx</span><br><span class="line">cd xxx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="git-上传"><a href="#git-上传" class="headerlink" title="git 上传"></a>git 上传</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git init //初始化</span><br><span class="line">git add ./ //把所有文件添加到暂存区</span><br><span class="line">git commit -m &quot;xxxxx&quot; </span><br><span class="line">git remote add origin https://githunb.com/用户名/abc.git</span><br><span class="line">git push -u //推送到仓库</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="托管到Cloudflare"><a href="#托管到Cloudflare" class="headerlink" title="托管到Cloudflare"></a>托管到Cloudflare</h2><p>登录Cloudflare控制台<br>Workers和Pages，创建应用程序，Pages，连接到Git，登录Github账户<br>同步所有仓库，或单独仓库，这里选择新创建的abc私有仓库<br>一路下一步，部署完成后，设置个人域名，方便访问</p><h2 id="git更新"><a href="#git更新" class="headerlink" title="git更新"></a>git更新</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git init </span><br><span class="line">git add ./</span><br><span class="line">git commit &quot;xxx&quot;</span><br><span class="line">git push -u </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>couldflare会自动同步内容</p><h3 id="完成✿✿ヽ-°▽°-ノ✿"><a href="#完成✿✿ヽ-°▽°-ノ✿" class="headerlink" title="完成✿✿ヽ(°▽°)ノ✿"></a>完成✿✿ヽ(°▽°)ノ✿</h3>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
