    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="添加标题"><a href="#添加标题" class="headerlink" title="添加标题"></a>添加标题</h2><p>添加xxx的标题，在index.html配置name文件</p><pre><code>window.$docsify = &#123;  name: &#39;xxx&#39;,&#125;</code></pre><h2 id="添加侧边"><a href="#添加侧边" class="headerlink" title="添加侧边"></a>添加侧边</h2><p>在index.html配置loadsidebar</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">window.$docsify = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  loadSidebar: true,</span><br><span class="line">   &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在目录下建立_sidebar.md文件</p><h2 id="添加顶栏"><a href="#添加顶栏" class="headerlink" title="添加顶栏"></a>添加顶栏</h2><pre><code>window.$docsify = &#123;  loadNavbar: true,    &#125;</code></pre><p>在目录下建立_navbar.md文件</p><h2 id="添加搜索"><a href="#添加搜索" class="headerlink" title="添加搜索"></a>添加搜索</h2><pre><code>window.$docsify = &#123;  search: &#123;    paths: &#39;auto&#39;,    placeholder: &#39;搜索&#39;,    noData: &#39;找不到结果&#39;,    depth: 3,    &#125;&#125;</code></pre>  <!-- 搜索插件 --><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;script src=&quot;//cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/docsify/lib/plugins/search.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt; </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="折叠目录"><a href="#折叠目录" class="headerlink" title="折叠目录"></a>折叠目录</h2><p>设置目录最大层级3</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">window.$docsify = &#123;</span><br><span class="line"> subMaxLevel: 3,</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="完成✿✿ヽ-°▽°-ノ✿"><a href="#完成✿✿ヽ-°▽°-ノ✿" class="headerlink" title=