    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="front-matter参数"><a href="#front-matter参数" class="headerlink" title="front-matter参数"></a>front-matter参数</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">layout布局</span><br><span class="line">title标题</span><br><span class="line">date建立日期</span><br><span class="line">updated更新日期</span><br><span class="line">comments开启文章的评论功能true</span><br><span class="line">tags标签（不适用于分页）</span><br><span class="line">categories分类（不适用于分页）</span><br><span class="line">permalink覆盖文章网址</span><br><span class="line">keywords仅用于 meta 标签和 Open Graph 的关键词（不推荐使用）</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="front-matter配置"><a href="#front-matter配置" class="headerlink" title="front-matter配置"></a>front-matter配置</h2><p>使用 hexo n “xxx” 新建一篇为xxx的文件</p><p>打开后显示内容</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">------------------------</span><br><span class="line">title: xxx</span><br><span class="line">date: 2024-01-01 01:00:00</span><br><span class="line">type: </span><br><span class="line">------------------------</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>即为front-matter</p><p>通过添加上面参数实现头文件的定义</p><h2 id="front-matter注意"><a href="#front-matter注意" class="headerlink" title="front-matter注意"></a>front-matter注意</h2><p>参数冒号后有空格<br>标签tags，需要配合建立标签page并在theme配置文件的menu中开启<br>分类categories，需要配合建立分类page并在theme配置文件的menu中开启<br>具体详见之前的文章<br>分类与标签可以有多个</p><p>标签</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">tags:</span><br><span class="line">- xxx</span><br><span class="line">- yyy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">categories：</span><br><span class="line">- aaa</span><br><span class="line">- bbb</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="开始写作✿✿ヽ-°▽°-ノ✿"><a href="#开始写作✿✿ヽ-°▽°-ノ✿" class="headerlink" title="开始写作✿✿ヽ(°▽°)ノ✿"></a>开始写作✿✿ヽ(°▽°)ノ✿</h3>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
