    <title>部署Hexo并托管到Github</title>
    <link href="https://blog.108186.xyz/2024/04/24/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2Hexo%E6%89%98%E7%AE%A1%E5%88%B0Github/"/>
    <id>https://blog.108186.xyz/2024/04/24/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2Hexo%E6%89%98%E7%AE%A1%E5%88%B0Github/</id>
    <published>2024-04-24T06:18:11.000Z</published>
    <updated>2024-05-08T09:24:16.965Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="安装环境"><a href="#安装环境" class="headerlink" title="安装环境"></a>安装环境</h2><h3 id="1-Mac下打开终端"><a href="#1-Mac下打开终端" class="headerlink" title="1.Mac下打开终端"></a>1.Mac下打开终端</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git --version</span><br><span class="line">nvm --version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果显示版本号则表示已安装</p><h3 id="2-如没安装"><a href="#2-如没安装" class="headerlink" title="2.如没安装"></a>2.如没安装</h3><p>下载Git<br><a href="https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https://git-scm.com/download/mac">https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//git-scm.com/download/mac</a></p><p>安装nvm</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/creationix/nvm/v0.33.2/install.sh | bash</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="环境配置"><a href="#环境配置" class="headerlink" title="环境配置"></a>环境配置</h2><h3 id="1-用vi创建文件并打开进行编辑"><a href="#1-用vi创建文件并打开进行编辑" class="headerlink" title="1.用vi创建文件并打开进行编辑"></a>1.用vi创建文件并打开进行编辑</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vi .bash_profile</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-粘贴代码"><a href="#2-粘贴代码" class="headerlink" title="2.粘贴代码"></a>2.粘贴代码</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">export NVM_DIR=&quot;$HOME/.nvm&quot;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[ -s &quot;$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh&quot; ] &amp;&amp; . &quot;$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-保存退出"><a href="#3-保存退出" class="headerlink" title="3.保存退出"></a>3.保存退出</h3><p>Shift+ZZ</p><h3 id="4-配置"><a href="#4-配置" class="headerlink" title="4.配置"></a>4.配置</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">source .bash_profile</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="安装Hexo"><a href="#安装Hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装Hexo"></a>安装Hexo</h2><h3 id="1-在桌面创建本地目录"><a href="#1-在桌面创建本地目录" class="headerlink" title="1.在桌面创建本地目录"></a>1.在桌面创建本地目录</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd ~/Desktop</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">mkdir hexo</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">cd hexo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-初始化"><a href="#2-初始化" class="headerlink" title="2.初始化"></a>2.初始化</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-报错"><a href="#3-报错" class="headerlink" title="3.报错"></a>3.报错</h3><p>可能是没有权限，按照报错提示进行授权即可</p><h3 id="4-本地启动"><a href="#4-本地启动" class="headerlink" title="4.本地启动"></a>4.本地启动</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo generate //生成静态网页 简写为 hexo g</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo server //运行hexo 简写为 hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="5-网页测试"><a href="#5-网页测试" class="headerlink" title="5.网页测试"></a>5.网页测试</h3><p><a href="http://localhost:4000/">http://localhost:4000</a></p><h3 id="6-新建一篇博客"><a href="#6-新建一篇博客" class="headerlink" title="6.新建一篇博客"></a>6.新建一篇博客</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo n “标题”</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在本地目录下的 &#x2F;source&#x2F;_post&#x2F; 会生成一个“标题.md”<br>使用Markdown语法编辑内容即可</p><h2 id="托管到Github"><a href="#托管到Github" class="headerlink" title="托管到Github"></a>托管到Github</h2><h3 id="1-新建仓库"><a href="#1-新建仓库" class="headerlink" title="1.新建仓库"></a>1.新建仓库</h3><p>打开<a href="https://github.com/%EF%BC%8C%E6%96%B0%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E4%BB%93%E5%BA%93New">https://github.com/，新建一个项目仓库New</a> repository<br>名字格式为name.github.io name必须与用户名一致</p><h3 id="2-修改配置"><a href="#2-修改配置" class="headerlink" title="2.修改配置"></a>2.修改配置</h3><p>打开本地目录下的_config.yml文件，并添加</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Deployment</span><br><span class="line">## Docs: https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment</span><br><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  type: git</span><br><span class="line">  repository: https://github.com/name/name.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">  branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-安装部署工具"><a href="#3-安装部署工具" class="headerlink" title="3.安装部署工具"></a>3.安装部署工具</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-设置身份令牌"><a href="#4-设置身份令牌" class="headerlink" title="4.设置身份令牌"></a>4.设置身份令牌</h3><p>由于Github安全机制，不能用密码直接git了</p><p>登录Github账户<br>生成新的token<br><a href="https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https://github.com/settings/tokens">https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//github.com/settings/tokens</a><br>note随便起，全部勾选，保存</p><h3 id="5-添加身份令牌"><a href="#5-添加身份令牌" class="headerlink" title="5.添加身份令牌"></a>5.添加身份令牌</h3><p>身份令牌每次有效期30天，每次更新都要输一遍，通过如下命令添加</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git remote set-url origin https://&lt;your_token&gt;@github.com/&lt;USERNAME&gt;/&lt;REPO&gt;.git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="三联更新"><a href="#三联更新" class="headerlink" title="三联更新"></a>三联更新</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo generate</span><br><span class="line">hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="完成✿✿ヽ-°▽°-ノ✿"><a href="#完成✿✿ヽ-°▽°-ノ✿" class="headerlink" title="完成✿✿ヽ(°▽°)ノ✿"></a>完成✿✿ヽ(°▽°)ノ✿</h3>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
